      • getPressureNum

        public int getPressureNum()
        Gets the number of the pressure data items. Normally, the number of the pressure data items matches with the sum of all dots constituting the stroke. However, the number of the pressure data items can be 0. Namely, the coordinate data of every dot constituting the stroke exists, but the pressure data may not be available.
        Returns:
